  planet: 1
  description: 
  descriptions:
  - "Planet Zim is an incredibly cold and barren planet. Most of it\u2019s residents
    and cities are underground."
  - The Zimians are a furry species with large and muscular arms, making their biology
    not well suited to the game of hexagonal archery. However, due to the prestige
    of this competition, Zim never misses the chance to participate in this competition,
    however unlikely it is for them to win.
  - 'The incredible viewership helps Zim show off their landscapes, especially their
    famous Zimian crystals which are sought after across the intergalactic empire. '
  - The zimians are known as a cold and isolationist planet and their main export
    is the Zimian crystal which is used for space travel.
